 Holi celebrations at Punjab Club, 10 am to 1 pm. Open to members and their guests only.

 Holi celebrations by Lok Sanskriti at IB Block community centre, Salt Lake, 8 am onwards on Saturday.

 On stage

 Three Acts, featuring Rupa Ganguly, Usha Uthup and Punam Singh, directed by Sujoy Prosad Chatterjee, will be presented by Patton, McDowell?s and The Park, in association with Open Doors, at The Park, 8 pm. Also on Saturday at Tollygunge Club, 7 pm.

 Art watch

 A group art exhibition at Idiyas Gallery, 10.30 am to 7.30 pm.

 Theatre

 Shouvanik will stage Brajo Sambad at Mukta Angan, 6.30 pm.

 Agaa at Academy of Fine Arts, 6.30 pm.

 Bilingual play Kamla at Gyan Manch, 6.30 pm on Saturday.




